    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以Dana Wallet先向Blindbit-Oracle发起订阅，然后Bitcoin Core Node把新区块推给Oracle？还是Oracle主动去轮询？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subscribe new blocks",
        "New Block"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是推送模式。Scanner先subscribe new blocks，然后Bitcoin Core Node把New Block推给Blindbit-Oracle。Oracle收到后要做三件事：compute tweak、index unspent outputs，还有build taproot GCS filter。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "subscribe new blocks",
        "New Block",
        "compute tweak",
        "index unspent outputs",
        "build taproot GCS filter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先把订阅和推送画出来。Oracle内部我加了两个自调用：compute tweak和compute spent，然后build taproot GCS filter。接下来Oracle把new block推回给Scanner？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "new block",
        "compute tweak",
        "compute spent",
        "build taproot GCS filter"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "compute spent应该是build taproot GCS filter之前的步骤，不是独立的自调用。顺序是：compute tweak、compute spent、然后build taproot GCS filter。另外Oracle推回Scanner时，Scanner会立即发起一个请求。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "compute tweak",
        "compute spent",
        "build taproot GCS filter",
        "Request tweaks & UTXOs for block"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "调整了，把compute spent放到build filter之前。然后Scanner发起Request tweaks & UTXOs for block，这里我标注一下关联Groupware IssueTracker的需求。Oracle返回Tweaks & relevant UTXOs。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request tweaks & UTXOs for block",
        "Tweaks & relevant UTXOs",
        "Groupware IssueTracker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有最后一步。Scanner需要再请求filters，拿到utxo and outpoint filters之后，自己在本地calculate UTXOs。这样整个流程闭环，钱包不需要暴露自己的地址给Oracle。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Request filters",
        "utxo and outpoint filters",
        "calculate UTXOs"
